results.title: The Last Titan
results.description: The last story of the Hulk.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 0
results.description: The Guardians of the Galaxy return to Earth and interrogate X-51.  Captain Marvel creates 7 angels out of the dead heroes to protect his Heaven in the Negative Zone.  Thor and Loki prepare to destroy Asgard.  Death abandons the Earth.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 1
results.description: Strange learns of Mephisto's plans.  Spider-Girl meets Venom

results.title: Paradise X Issue 10
results.description: Captain America frees the Dead from Paradise.  Mephisto steals Excalibur from Captain Britain and impales him with it.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 11
results.description: Mephisto conquers the British court.  Mr. Fantastic enters the Paradise.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 12
results.description: Merlin, Strange, Psylocke, Captain Britain and the Deviants wage a final battle with Mephisto.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 2
results.description: The Punisher is attacked by his dead enemies.  Mar-Vell's Paradise encroaches on the Negative Zone.  Karnak battles the Guardians of the Galaxy

results.title: Paradise X Issue 3
results.description: King Britain is married to Medusa.  The Grey Gargoyle returns.  Captain America tracks down the Skull in Paradise.

results.title: Paradise X Chapter 4
results.description: The Paradise comes under attack from the Negative Zone.  X-51 reveals that the animalistic mutants, such as Wolverine, are actually part of a different species.  The Grey Gargoyle frees Excalibur.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 5
results.description: Mr. Fantastic and his allies plan to recreate Death.  Meggan is reunited with King Britain.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 6
results.description: The Guardians of the Galaxy battle Blastaar and Annihilus.  Wolverine returns to the wild.  The Punisher murders his family again in the paradise.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 7
results.description: Mephisto releases Jude.  Captain America talks about the afterlife with Thanos.  The Punisher is let loose in Paradise.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 8
results.description: Jude attacks the heroes in Latveria.  Iron Maiden begins a quest to find the Eternals.  Mr. Fantastic builds an army to enter the Negative Zone.  Thor prepares to go to war with Odin.

results.title: Paradise X Issue 9
results.description: Captain America awakens the Red Skull.  Captain Britain choses Medusa over Meggan.  Mr. Fantastic's army finds the Paradise.

results.title: Paradise X Issue X
results.description: The Dead battle the Kree to save the Paradise.  The purpose of the Paradise is revealed.  Mr. Fantastic evolves into the new Eternity.

results.title: Savage Genesis
results.description: Rogue's nightmares lead the X-Men to a race of saurian dinosaur people who are being hunted; The X-Folk decide to give them a hand in making it to the Savage Land.

results.title: Deluge
results.description: The X-Men escape a tidal wave to get the Saurids to the Savage Land; Brainchild captures Storm; Lupa enslaves Beast to her will.

results.title: False Haven !
results.description: Brainchild causes dissention between the humans and the saurians and a war breaks out; Brainchild reverts Storm to a feral form.

results.title: What Price, Freedom? What Price, Humanity?
results.description: The X-Men beat Brainchild and his Mutates and reunite the humans and saurians in peace.

X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 4 (2009)

results.title: With Great Power ...
results.description: The Marvel heroes join the X-Men in an all out attack on Onslaught; Many of the non-mutant heroes are forced to sacrifice themselves to beat their foe; The battle is won, but at the ultimate cost.

items.name: X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 4 (2009)
X-Men: The Complete Onslaught Epic Vol. 4 (2009)

results.title: Ascendance
results.description: Magneto arrives in Genosha as its new monarch with a civil war between Magistrates and mutates in full swing; Quicksilver shows up in Genosha to confront his father but is captured by rebel mutates who want to keep their land from Maggie; Rogue joins the party as well.

results.title: Has the Prodigal Son Returned...To Face His Death?
Into Darkness
results.description: Rogue and Amelia rescue Quicksilver from the mutates; Magneto prepares to take his new monarchy from all who oppose him.

results.title: Once We Were Kings
results.description: Magneto quells the rebellion and begins to rule Genosha with Quicksilver and Vogt at his side.
